name: Women's 'Gunner' Jacket (Caldari)
description: Advertise your stature as the terror of the celestial skies in this sleek, comfortable jacket. A solid blue front with outlines of a rising pillar serve to underline your undeniable and unyielding presence, while pitch black sleeves give you the commanding appearance you deserve. Finally, the logo of the Caldari State advertises your proud support for the only faction that matters.
